                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-739630608" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="739630608">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jinkai719/">阅微草堂</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-10-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实感觉就是一个博士论文，水平太过于普通，文笔过于啰嗦，在试图可读性和理论性之间打着秋千。人文学科或者是精神学科必须有所命题局限性</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="470364428">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-470364428" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-470364428" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="470364428">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/renqiran/">Bricoleur</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-10-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读完之后去拿了点果酱吃面包，突然间觉得这个搭配口感不一样了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="616424655">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-616424655" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-616424655" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="616424655">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xuduo1989/">攸川</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">据说物质文化研究的经典之作。蔗糖生产跟资本主义早期在西印度群岛的奴隶制种植园有关。通过追溯糖的历史为资本主义发展又提供了一个生动的例证，but，so what？太学术的操作，冲击力不够，甚至显得啰嗦。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

